verbose_text: These results suggested that the CC-CSS + ICT could quickly reduce penile rigidity and pain of PIP, however, erectile dysfunction due to sever corpus carvernosum fibrosis post CC-CSS + ICT significantly influence QOL of patients and penile prosthesis implantation is a safe and effective method for treating ED for post CC-CSS + ICT.
evidence: ICT could quickly reduce penile rigidity and pain of PIP
